{
  "topic_id": "4_3",
  "title": "使用 Flex 布局构建响应式导航栏",
  "description_md": "使用 Flexbox 布局创建一个响应式导航栏。\n\n- 请为 `nav` 元素设置 `display: flex`，并使用 `justify-content: space-around` 实现导航项等间距分布\n- 设置 `gap: 20px` 使导航项之间有统一间距\n- 使用 `flex-wrap: wrap` 允许导航项在小屏幕下自动换行",
  "start_code": {
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>编程学习导航栏</title>\n  <style>\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n      background-color: #f0f8ff;\n      color: #333;\n    }\n    nav a {\n      text-decoration: none;\n      padding: 10px 15px;\n      background-color: #007acc;\n      color: white;\n      border-radius: 5px;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h3>编程学习教程</h3>\n    <nav>\n      <a href=\"#\">首页</a>\n      <a href=\"#\">课程</a>\n      <a href=\"#\">资源</a>\n      <a href=\"#\">社区</a>\n      <a href=\"#\">关于我们</a>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n  <section>\n    <p>欢迎来到编程学习平台，这里提供丰富的编程资源和实战项目。</p>\n  </section>\n  <footer>\n    <p>© 2025 编程学习平台 - 教学用途</p>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "css": "",
    "js": ""
  },
  "checkpoints": [
    {
      "name": "导航栏使用 Flex 布局",
      "type": "assert_style",
      "selector": "nav",
      "css_property": "display",
      "assertion_type": "equals",
      "value": "flex",
      "feedback": "请为 nav 设置 display: flex。"
    },
    {
      "name": "导航项等间距分布",
      "type": "assert_style",
      "selector": "nav",
      "css_property": "justify-content",
      "assertion_type": "equals",
      "value": "space-around",
      "feedback": "请设置 nav 的 justify-content 为 space-around。"
    },
    {
      "name": "导航项允许换行",
      "type": "assert_style",
      "selector": "nav",
      "css_property": "flex-wrap",
      "assertion_type": "equals",
      "value": "wrap",
      "feedback": "请确保 nav 设置了 flex-wrap: wrap。"
    },
    {
      "name": "导航项间距设置",
      "type": "assert_style",
      "selector": "nav",
      "css_property": "gap",
      "assertion_type": "equals",
      "value": "20px",
      "feedback": "请为 nav 设置 gap 为 20px。"
    }
  ]
}